| Area               | Key Points |
|--------------------|------------|
| CIA Triad          | Confidentiality, Integrity, Availability |
| Risk Mgmt           | Identify, Assess, Treat, Monitor |
| Control Types       | Administrative, Technical, Physical |
| Code of Ethics      | 4 Canons |
| Governance Elements | Policy, Standard, Procedure, Regulation, Law |

